            "creation_date": 1393824718,
            "body": "<p>Change it by from<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>    &lt;uses-permission android:name=\"INTERNET\"/&gt;\n    &lt;uses-permission android:name=\"ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE\"/&gt;\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>to<\/p>\n\n<pre><code>   &lt;uses-permission android:name=\"android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE\" /&gt;\n   &lt;uses-permission android:name=\"android.permission.INTERNET\" /&gt;\n<\/code><\/pre>\n\n<p>Also you have to clean your project and rebuild it again. Also uninstall your app from device. And finally must insure that in your mobile device internet is available.<\/p>\n",
